socialTags.og:title: DALLE Food and Restaurant
socialTags.og:description: DALLE is one of the fastest-growing quick-service restaurants (QSR) in Nepal. Dalle presents you Darjeeling-style cooked food, which is a very basic and simple style of cooking with core ingredients that are the hero of the dish, and bursts of natural flavors.
socialTags.keywords: Dalle Nepal, Food Delivery, Momos, Dalle Bowl, Dalle Achar, Nepalese cuisine, Dalle Kathmandu, Dalle Pokhara, Best Momos, Quality Food.
socialTags.description: Tantalize your palate with our delicious and true flavored Darjeeling-style cooked food. Dalle is one of the most popular go-to places for momo. Dalle also offers catering and meal box services. Dalle has a total of 11 outlets to choose from with the best services and offers. Dalle offers you quality delivery services within Nepal right at your doorsteps.
